 "imp-f-danseuse-de-ballet": "An alternative ballet dance.",
 "imp-f-danseuses-des-rues": "Three young women dance in Drury Lane, London.",
 "imp-f-das-boxende-k-nguruh": "A man and a kangaroo stand up in front of each other with boxing gloves, and simulate a boxing match on a theatre stage.",
 "imp-f-daylight": "A group of armed robbers fleeing the police head for the New Jersey Tunnel and run right into trucks transporting toxic waste. The spectacular explosion that follows results in both ends of the tunnel collapsing and the handful of people who survived the explosion are now in peril. Kit Latura is the only man with the skill and knowledge to lead the band of survivors out of the tunnel before the structure collapses.",
 "imp-f-demolition-man": "In 1996, brash L.A. detective John Spartan and maniac killer Simon Phoenix are both sentenced to decades in a cryogenic prison as punishment for a rescue mission gone wrong. When Phoenix escapes 36 years later to wreak havoc on the future, Spartan is awakened to capture his nemesis the old-fashioned way.",
 "imp-f-descente-de-la-grande-pyramide": "Descent of the Great Pyramid.",
 "imp-s-259066": "Are you ready for another batch of detective puzzles?",
 "imp-s-96171": "Dexter, a boy-genius with a secret laboratory, constantly battles his sister Dee Dee, who always gains access despite his best efforts to keep her out, as well as his arch-rival and neighbor, Mandark.",
 "imp-f-dickson-experimental-sound-film": "William K.L. Dickson plays the violin while two men dance. This is the oldest surviving sound film where sound is recorded on the phonograph.",
 "imp-f-dickson-greeting": "William K.L. Dickson brings his hat from his one hand to the other and moves his head slightly, as a small nod toward the audience. This was the first film produced by the Edison Manufacturing Company to be shown to public audiences and the press.",
 "imp-s-229926": "Dino Babies is a family-friendly educational cartoon spotlighting six young dinosaurs who share stories and adventures.",
 "imp-f-doctor-dolittle": "A successful physician and devoted family man, John Dolittle seems to have the world by the tail, until a long suppressed talent he possessed as a child, the ability to communicate with animals is suddenly reawakened with a vengeance! Now every creature within squawking distance wants the good doctor's advice, unleashing an outrageous chain of events that turns his world upside down!",
 "imp-f-double-jeopardy": "Libby Parsons, wrongly convicted of her husband Nick's murder, thinks he is still alive. She survives the long years in prison with two burning desires sustaining her -- finding her son and solving the mystery that destroyed her once-happy life. Standing between her and her quest, however, is her parole officer, Travis Lehman. Libby poses a challenge to the cynical officer, one that forces him to face up to his own failings while pitting him against his superior and law enforcement colleagues, as she plunges into a desperate fight for justice, survival, and revenge.",
 "imp-f-douche-apr-s-le-bain": "Four young people throwing buckets of water at each other.",
 "imp-f-dragons-traversant-la-sa-ne-la-nage": "A stationary camera looks across Burgundy's river Sâone toward a small military encampment. Four horsemen enter the water in the foreground, each riding his horse as it swims across toward camp or leading it by the bridle as they swim",
 "imp-f-drat-that-boy": "A boy pulls a prank on his poor old mother.",
 "imp-f-dresden-august-br-cke": "A short film from the Lumière brothers, filmed in a Dresden street.",
 "imp-s-163766": "Duck Dodgers battles evil in the 24th century.",
 "imp-s-96106": "Scrooge McDuck finds his hands full at home when nephews Huey, Dewey and Louie move to Duckburg. Joined by their loyal pals Launchpad McQuack, Gyro Gearloose and Mrs. Beakley, the DuckTales gang never fails to deliver a wealth of adventure. Get ready for a fortune of fun with DuckTales!",
 "imp-f-duel-au-pistolet": "Based on a real event that occurred between two deputies, in Chapultepec Park.",
